         <div type="translation">
            <p>[The sarcophagus and] the place on which the sarcophagus is placed and the burial nichesbelong to Mar[cus Aurelius Apollo]nios son of Demetrios son of Apollonios <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> and his wife Aurelia <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
            </p>
